# IntelliJ build output
**/out/

# Compiled bytecode
*.class

# Generated API specs (can be regenerated from /v3/api-docs)
knowledge_back/docs/openapi.json
knowledge_back/docs/openapi.yaml

# If you also want to ignore packaged jars (optional)
# knowledge_back/target/*.jar

